    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-cpb-dr-01",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels under MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for MRL 2 Class II devices. The CFD model demonstrates adequate credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy RH < 1 across all five operating points with agreement within 8.7% of experimental measurements. The assessment team concludes the model is fit for the stated context of use.",
